      <b>External Storage</b><p>You can also integrate HPE Storevirtual 4000-series or HPE StoreServ
        (3PAR) storage in the KVM Region. </p><p>You must install 3PAR or Storevirtual before
        starting the HP Helion OpenStack installation and are independent of HP Helion OpenStack
        Carrier Grade. During the installation, you will integrate the storage into HP Helion
        OpenStack Carrier Grade. See the installation instructions for the 3PAR and/or Storvirtual
        parameters you will
      need.</p><!--<p id="tahoe"><b>KVM with DCN Topology using the Tahoe Deployment</b></p><p>If you are installing the Tahoe deployment, you are installing the KVM Region and <xref href="../Overview/carrier-grade-overview.dita#topic4010/networking">HP Distributed Cloud Networking VRS networking (DCN VRS)</xref>. </p><p>You can also integrate HPE Storevirtual (VSA) or HPE StoreServ (3PAR) storage in the KVM Region. </p><p>You must install DCN, 3PAR or VSA before starting the HP Helion OpenStack installation and are independent of HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. During the installation, you will integrate the storage into HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. See the <xref href="tahoe/CGH-2-install-tahoe.dita#topic10581c2it/storage">installation instructions</xref> for the 3PAR and/or VSA parameters you will need.</p><p>Start <xref href="tahoe/carrier-grade-install-overview-tahoe.dita#topic1925cgiot">installing the Tahoe deployment</xref>.</p>--><!--<p id="memphis"><b>KVM + ESX with DCN Topology using the Memphis Deployment</b></p><p>If you are installing the Memphis deployment, you are installing the KVM Region and VMware ESX storage. The networking uses <xref href="../Overview/carrier-grade-overview.dita#topic4010/networking">HP DCN VRS</xref>. This deployment allows you to manage the KVM and VMware ESX<tm tmtype="reg"/> hypervisors.</p><p>You can also integrate HPE Storevirtual (VSA) or HPE StoreServ (3PAR) storage in the KVM Region. </p><p>You must install DCN, ESX, and 3PAR and/or VSA before starting the HP Helion OpenStack installation and are independent of HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. During the installation, you will integrate the storage into HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. See the <xref href="memphis/CGH-2-install-memphis.dita#topic10581c2im/storage">installation instructions</xref> for the 3PAR and/or VSA parameters you will need.</p><p>You will need to perform tasks to integrate ESX and DCN with HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. These steps are described during this installation process.</p>Start <xref href="memphis/carrier-grade-install-overview-memphis.dita#topic1925cgiom">installing the Memphis deployment</xref>.--><!--<p id="sacramento"><b>KVM + ESX + Ironic with DCN Topology using the Sacramento Deployment</b></p><p>If you are installing the Sacramento deployment, you are installing the KVM Region, VMware ESX storage, and a baremetal region (controlled by OpenStack Ironic). The networking uses <xref href="../Overview/carrier-grade-overview.dita#topic4010/networking">HP DCN VRS</xref>. This deployment allows you to manage the KVM and VMware ESX<tm tmtype="reg"/> hypervisors.</p><p>You can also integrate HPE Storevirtual (VSA) or HPE StoreServ (3PAR) storage in the KVM Region. </p><p>You must install DCN, ESX, and 3PAR and/or VSA before starting the HP Helion OpenStack installation and are independent of HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. During the installation, you will integrate the storage into HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. See the <xref href="sacramento/CGH-2-install-sacramento.dita#topic10581c2is/backend">installation instructions</xref> for the 3PAR and/or VSA parameters you will need.</p>You will need to perform tasks to integrate ESX and DCN with HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade. These steps are described during this installation process.<p>Start <xref href="sacramento/carrier-grade-install-overview-sacramento.dita#topic1925cgios">installing the Sacramento deployment</xref>.</p>--></section>
